.mui-container
  .mui-row
    .mui-col-md-12.mui-col-xs-12
      h1 Connection Requests


- @connection_requests.each do |connection_request|
  .mui-container
    = render 'connection_requests/info', connection_request: connection_request
    = render 'connection_requests/action_buttons', connection_request: connection_request
    = render 'connection_requests/relation_buttons', connection_request: connection_request

.mui-container
  .mui-row
    .mui-col-md-12.mui-col-xs-12
      - if @connection_requests.empty?
        em There are no connection requests to show.

.form-section
= paginate @connection_requests
